<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 21 at 12:25PM CDT  by NWS QuadCities</headline>
<description>...Heat Index Readings 94 to 99 This Afternoon...
Heat index readings will top out in the mid to upper 90s across
much of the area this afternoon.
If you will be spending time outdoors this afternoon, be sure to
stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water, and take frequent
breaks in shaded areas or in an air conditioned building. Also,
be sure to look before you lock! Don`t leave your pets or kids in
a parked car.</description>
